<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa ʋba Mi̱ko ma!
 Chishno poyulla kak ocha
 Ik yohmi, ish aiahni ho̱,
 Nana moma kʋt toba tok.

[V2]
 Yʋmohmi pulla tuk oka,
 Nan okcha̱ya moyuma kʋt
 Chi ahnihinchi pulla cha,
 Pit chi aiokpahanchashke.

[V3]
 Hatak, oklushi puyuta,
 Enchil moma aiena kʋt
 Ʋba i̱ Mi̱ko chia ka
 Pit chi aiokpahanchashke.

[V4]
 Ish pi̱ hullo hatuk mak o̱,
 Ilhfiopak atukmʋto
 Pin takanli moma hocha,
 Pit e chi ahnihinchishke.

[V5]
 5 Yohmi tuk osh hʋp illikmʋt
 Ish ai ʋtta il ona cha,
 E chi aiokpahanchi kʋt
 E bilia he mak oke.</lyrics>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Chihowa ʋba Mi̱ko ma ƲIT2</title>
